author: Reuters Editorial
title: CORRECTED (OFFICIAL)-BRIEF-OUE Announces Subscription of shares in Pt. Oue Property Development and Pt. Oue Pengembangan Properti
text:
(Corrects subscription amount in text to S$1.1 mln from S$1 bln after company corrects value; changes source link)
April 30 (Reuters) - OUE Ltd:
* UNIT SUBSCRIBED FOR 99.9 PERCENT SHARES IN EACH OF PT. OUE PROPERTY DEVELOPMENT AND PT. OUE PENGEMBANGAN PROPERTI FOR S$1.1 MILLION EACH Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
